comment: Clarkson (LAL) extends his arm into Kilpatrick (BKN) to create space.
[Observable in enhanced video] Clarkson (LAL) moves his pivot foot. The official is refereeing the defenders and looking for any potential illegal contact and does not pick up the pivot foot.
Bass (LAL) maintains a legal guarding position on the drive to the basket and shot attempt by Young (BKN).
Bass (LAL) maintains a legal guarding position as he defends Bogdanovic (BKN) on the perimeter. The contact on the play is initiated by Bogdanovic.
Randle (LAL) sets the screen on Kilpatrick (BKN) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Sloan (BKN) commits a take foul on Bass (LAL).
Young (BKN) sets the screen on Russell (LAL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.

RHH shows that Randle (LAL) maintains a legal guarding position as he defends Sloan's (BKN) driving shot attempt and any contact on the play is initiated by Sloan. After the shot attempt has been released, Bass (LAL) makes incidental "high five" contact.
Young (BKN) commits a take foul on Randle (LAL).
Sloan (BKN) commits a take foul on Russell (LAL).
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Ellington (BKN) did not release the ball prior to the clock expiring was confirmed.
